setup.lua
content:
--[[
    label set <task name>
    pastebin run PtV2LYTL <host url prefix> <auth token>
]]

local tArgs = { ... }
if #tArgs ~= 2 then
    error("usage: pastebin run <pastebin id> <host url prefix> <auth token>")
end

local host = tArgs[1]
local auth = tArgs[2]
local filename = "startup.lua"
local label = os.getComputerLabel()

local response = http.get {
    url = host .. filename,
    headers = {
        ["X-Auth"] = auth,
        ["User-Agent"] = "ComputerCraft (setup:" .. label .. ")",
    },
}

if response then
    local code = response.getResponseCode()
    if code == 200 then
        local data = response.readAll()
        response.close()
        local f = fs.open("/" .. filename, "w")
        f.write(data)
        f.close()
        os.reboot()
    else
        error("Failed to download " .. host .. filename .. " with code " .. code)
    end
end

error("Failed to download " .. host .. filename .. " with nil response")
